quran[6{c,v,t}:
6,119,"aakhir kya wajah hai ke tum woh cheez nah khao jis par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho, halaank jin cheezon ka istemaal haalat iztarar ke siwa doosri tamam halaton mein Allah ne haraam kar diya hai unn ki tafseel woh tumhe bta chuka hai bakasrat logon ka haal yeh hai ke ilm ke baghair mehez apni khwahisaat ki bana par gumraah kin baatein karte hain, un hadd se guzarnay walon ko tumhara rab khoob jaanta hai"
6,120,"tum khulay gunaaho se bhi bachcho aur chupay gunaaho se bhi, jo log gunah ka Iktisab karte hain woh apni is kamaai ka badla paker rahen ge"
6,121,"aur jis janwar ko Allah ka naam le kar zibah nah kya gaya ho is ka gosht nah khao, aisa karna fisq hai shyatin apne sathiyon ke dilon mein shukook o aitrazaat alqa karte hain taakay woh tum se jhagra karen lekin agar tum ne unn ki itaat qubool kar li to yaqeenan tum mushriq ho"
6,122,kya woh shakhs jo pehlay murda tha phir hum ne usay zindagi bakhsh aur is ko woh roshni ataa ki jis ke ujalay mein woh logon ke darmain zindagi ki raah tey karta hai uss shakhs ki terhan ho sakta hai jo tarikeon mein para howa ho aur kisi terhan unn se nah nikalta ho? kafiroon ke liye to isi terhan un ke aamaal khushnuma bana diye gay hain
6,123,"aur isi terhan hum ne har bastii mein is ke barray barray mujrimon ko laga diya hai ke wahan apne makr o fraib ka jaal philayin darasal woh apne fraib ke jaal mein aap phnste hain, magar unhen is ka shaoor nahi hai"
6,124,"jab un ke samnay koi aayat aati hai to woh kehte hain"" hum nah manen ge jab taq ke woh cheez khud hum ko nah di jaye jo Allah ke Rasolo-n ko di gayi hai"" Allah ziyada behtar jaanta hai ke apni peghambari ka kaam kis se le aur kis terhan le qareeb hai woh waqt jab yeh mujrim apni mkaryon ki Padaash mein Allah ke haan zillat aur sakht azaab se do chaar hon ge"
